[Socioeconomic aspects of the treatment of arrhythmias].

[Article in German]

Neuzner J(1), Carlsson J.

Author information:
(1)Abteilung für Kardiologie, Kerckhoff-Klinik Bad Nauheim. 
joerg.neuzner@kerckhoff.med.uni-giessen.de

In the current clinical cardiac electrophysiology well-defined and effective 
